 <br />\n但歷史真係冇如果<br />\n再打上去金軍有冇機會反撲真係唔知<br />\n另外有一點好重要嘅係完顏阿骨打完全冇把握滅，所以先接受議和"},{"pid":"96ba82397d267a4b0af35e1148bd956aaa4fef6f","tid":40249,"uid":2295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T06:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>究竟如果宋高宗條廢鳩 (佢條鳩係真係廢左) 唔撚阻止中興四傑打上去, 我大宋有冇機光後幽燕?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雖然我都好想知岳飛班友收唔收復到燕雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但歷史真係冇如果<br />\n再打上去金軍有冇機會反撲真係唔知<br />\n另外有一點好重要嘅係完顏阿骨打完全冇把握滅，所以先接受議和</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個陣金兵仲未完全收皮<br />\n騎兵仲有一半既<br />\n不過以岳家軍既戰力同岳飛既<br />\n一貫戰績同咁熟悉金兵<br />\n<br />\n其實北上收復贏既可能性都真係幾大"},{"pid":"66df6b8278ca0b65cd65585046f94064243af43f","tid":40249,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:22:14.000Z","msg":"大石打死蒙哥，救埋歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a596a8ba1d80f1778dd5cb5c85f27309af68a908","tid":40249,"uid":14716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大石打死蒙哥，救埋歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁歐洲今日就仲係落後第三世界國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e730a770bfe0f781ab7ee39cdb3bb5cb23fef7b5","tid":40249,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:42:06.000Z","msg":"宋朝post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n華麗留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f42ca2111487776bd063aea4a7521ed7222bf7","tid":40249,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T15:54:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>大石打死蒙哥，救埋歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁歐洲今日就仲係落後第三世界國家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打埋日本統一全球, 大家都係蒙古人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e76025807ca7fac631619382cf9c88d9cbb94ec3","tid":40249,"uid":29260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T18:07:55.000Z","msg":"放低史學太耐，好多都記唔起。<br />\n<br />\n其實北宋輸係太遲搞改革，先唔好講得唔得，開國至神宗果陣有太多為改五代十國遺風而做既野，就係令宋積弱。<br />\n<br />\n無左幽燕，定都汴京，都唔係令軍事積弱主因。要知道宋代議和咁耐都仲係有錢，其實問題都係太重文輕武，太怕武人奪權，搞個「將軍輪換，強幹弱枝，增民不練兵」，再有幾勁既將，幾好既戰術，幾好既裝備都無用。一個文官做紙上談兵既指揮都玩死你。<br />\n<br />\n聯金滅遼已經夠笨，前車可鑒都仲要去聯蒙滅金。<br />\n<br />\n宋代以降，中國真係可以話咩文明都徒具空殻"},{"pid":"dcd21d35ff0e99c27a21fc0345a10b4f3f219771","tid":40249,"uid":65198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T19:58:53.000Z","msg":"奧比旺巴打好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之前係明朝個post 見過巴打"},{"pid":"3c920e6d515a1dd6f066bd249da87bad7d47c4b2","tid":40249,"uid":65198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T20:14:40.000Z","msg":"兩宋並非書上所述如此無能 <br />\n<br />\n有與趣既巴打可以睇下日本人對宋的看法 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://wechat.kanfb.com/archives/256118\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwechat.kanfb.com%2Farchives%2F256118&d=pnoFg8kAQ%2F%2F%2BYzMoxsNoToscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=e9f8043c\" target=\"_blank\">http://wechat.kanfb.com/archives/256118</a><br />\n<br />\n個時中史老師教宋個時俾我地睇 顛覆左我對宋的睇法 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23ae613c2641a65ec664c21f29e921c4b0567cf","tid":40249,"uid":37264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:00:48.000Z","msg":"北宋王安石變法可以話係北宋政治既分水嶺。<br />\n如果唔係介甫兄牌氣大, 神宗玩野, 加埋之後哲宗死得早,<br />\n北宋改革成到形真係不得了"},{"pid":"7bbfbea5c60cee994f947d4622ab4cc5f276915b","tid":40249,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T02:59:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>兩宋並非書上所述如此無能 <br />\n<